{"id":409131,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/88/318858.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"班固米做菜人","groupHref":"/group/zuocai","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/43/4324.jpg?r=1574965416","message":"每到秋天，超市就会开始卖柿子。昨天买了一颗将近400g重的大柿子，从网上看到烤柿子的食谱，在家尝试了一下。<br><br>【材料】<br><br>柿子 1个（选择脆柿子，软柿子不太行）<br>黄油 10g（没有也行）<br><br><img src=\"https://ako445.github.io/sharing/pics/20241107/cleaned_photo_2024-11-07_18-52-28.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>【制作步骤】<br><br>1. 柿子去蒂，用刀从顶部将果肉切出米字形的切口。注意不要切破柿子下半部分的表皮。<br><br><img src=\"https://ako445.github.io/sharing/pics/20241107/cleaned_photo_2024-11-07_18-52-30.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>2. 烤箱预热。把柿子放入烤箱中，180度加热15分钟。<br><br><img src=\"https://ako445.github.io/sharing/pics/20241107/cleaned_photo_2024-11-07_18-52-31.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>3. 放上黄油，继续加热两三分钟至黄油融化。<br><br><img src=\"https://ako445.github.io/sharing/pics/20241107/cleaned_photo_2024-11-07_18-52-33.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>4. 出锅。<br><br><img src=\"https://ako445.github.io/sharing/pics/20241107/cleaned_photo_2024-11-07_18-52-34.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br><img src=\"https://ako445.github.io/sharing/pics/20241107/cleaned_photo_2024-11-07_18-52-36.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><br>柿子加热后质地变软，比直接吃更甜，而且意外地和黄油的口味很协调 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/46.gif\" smileid=\"85\" alt=\"(bgm69)\"><br><br>值得一试 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">","time":"2024-11-7 18:20","title":"烤柿子","userId":"koimxj","userName":"Komeiji💤","userSign":"(病める時も健やかなる時も朝も昼も夜も夢も現もずっと)"}